text.text:
People say this Italian restaurant serves delicious crab linguini, caponata, tuna carpaccio, and beef tartare. They also highlight the beautiful design, spacious layout, and authentic Italian cuisine.

Other reviews mention the staff can be inattentive.

originalText.text: We stayed at Middle 8 for 2 nights with our two daughters just before Christmas. We didn't want to go fancy restaurants with the kids, so we had dinner here both nights. The food was way above my expectations. The chef Andrea was amazing and he gave us some recommendations what's best and what to try. Literally all dishes were faultless, the presentation and taste were fantastic. The best dish was probably the crab squid ink tagliatelle. The kids loved the chicken Milanese. Highly recommended restaurant. Keep up the good work!

originalText.text: Came to celebrate my friends birthday dinner and was wonderful. Service was amazing particularly Benedicte who went beyond to make it a memorable dinner by helping with pictures and assisting. The food was also lovely and worth the money! They ended up surprising us with a cake for my friend on her bday on the house which was very thoughtful.

A wonderful experience.
Alex took excellent care of us from the moment we arrived.
Food was delicious, the whole team was very friendly and the environment was very relaxing and nice.
I would definitely go back to this place.
They welcomed us with a big smile and the deal that we had offered a perfect value for money experience!
